    {
      "id": "boxjs_to_ql",
      "name": "boxjs同步ql",
      "descs_html": [
        "<b>支持两种模式，请根据需求填写：</b>",
        "<b>1. 通用配置：</b>如果所有面板的端口、Client ID、Secret都相同，则在对应输入框各填写一个通用值即可。",
        "<b>2. 独立配置：</b>如果每个面板的配置都不同，请在IP、端口、Client ID、Secret输入框中分别填入多个值，用英文符号 '@' 分隔，并确保各项顺序一一对应。",
        "青龙 docker 作者仓库：【<a href=\"https://github.com/whyour\">github</a>】",
        "青龙 docker 频道：【<a href=\"https://t.me/jiao_long\">电报频道</a>】"
      ],
      "keys": [
        "@ql.mute",
        "@ql.sync_env__key",
        "@ql.ip",
        "@ql.port",
        "ql.baseUrl",
        "@ql.client_id",
        "@ql.client_secret"
      ],
      "settings": [
        {
          "id": "@ql.mute",
          "name": "静音通知",
          "val": false,
          "type": "boolean",
          "persistentHint": true,
          "desc": "同步完成后，是否关闭系统通知。"
        },
        {
          "id": "@ql.sync_env__key",
          "name": "同步环境变量规则",
          "val": "",
          "type": "textarea",
          "placeholder": "boxjs变量名#ql变量名#ql备注-boxjs变量名#ql变量名#ql备注 (禁用)",
          "rows": 5,
          "autoGrow": true,
          "persistentHint": true,
          "desc": "定义需要同步的变量规则，每行一条。行首加'-'可禁用该条规则。"
        },
        {
          "id": "@ql.ip",
          "name": "青龙面板 IP 地址",
          "val": "",
          "type": "textarea",
          "placeholder": "例如: 192.168.1.10@192.168.1.11或者http://192.168.1.10@http://192.168.1.11",
          "rows": 1,
          "autoGrow": true,
          "persistentHint": true,
          "desc": "支持多个IP，用'@'分隔。"
        },
        {
          "id": "@ql.port",
          "name": "青龙面板端口",
          "val": "",
          "type": "textarea",
          "placeholder": "通用则填一个: 5700独立则填多个: 5700@5701",
          "rows": 1,
          "autoGrow": true,
          "persistentHint": true,
          "desc": "如果通用，只需填写一个。如果独立，用'@'分隔并与IP顺序对应。"
        },
        {
          "id": "ql.baseUrl",
          "name": "青龙基础URL",
          "val": "",
          "type": "text",
          "persistentHint": false,
          "desc": ""
        },
        {
          "id": "@ql.client_id",
          "name": "青龙面板 Client ID",
          "val": "",
          "type": "textarea",
          "placeholder": "通用则填一个: a1b2c3d4独立则填多个: a1b2c3d4@e5f6g7h8",
          "rows": 1,
          "autoGrow": true,
          "persistentHint": true,
          "desc": "如果通用，只需填写一个。如果独立，用'@'分隔并与IP顺序对应。"
        },
        {
          "id": "@ql.client_secret",
          "name": "青龙面板 Client Secret",
          "val": "",
          "type": "textarea",
          "placeholder": "通用则填一个: x1y2z3独立则填多个: x1y2z3@w4v5u6",
          "rows": 1,
          "autoGrow": true,
          "persistentHint": true,
          "desc": "如果通用，只需填写一个。如果独立，用'@'分隔并与IP顺序对应。"
        }
      ],
      "scripts": [
        {
          "name": "同步变量",
          "script": "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/fly818/QX/master/Script/boxjs_to_ql.js",
          "iCloudPath": "boxjs_to_ql.js"
        }
      ],
      "author": "mumu",
      "repo": "https://github.com/fly818/QX/blob/master/Script/boxjs_to_ql.js",
      "icons": [
        "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/WowYiJiu/Personal/main/icon/Alpha/ql.png",
        "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/WowYiJiu/Personal/main/icon/Color/ql.png"
      ]
    },
